_ms": 8530, "end_ms": 9490, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "不構成投資建議", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 4, "start_ms": 9490, "end_ms": 11570, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "好 我們今天視頻可能會稍微短一點", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 5, "start_ms": 11570, "end_ms": 13490, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "首先來看一下今天的盤面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 6, "start_ms": 13490, "end_ms": 17410, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "盤面當中我們看到今天整個分值是比較低的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 7, "start_ms": 17410, "end_ms": 20490, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個是今天看起來整個市場比較差的一面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 8, "start_ms": 20490, "end_ms": 22810, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但好的一面今天漲的個戶還是比較多", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 9, "start_ms": 22810, "end_ms": 24250, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "3351個在漲", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 10, "start_ms": 24240, "end_ms": 25840, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "2098個在低", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 11, "start_ms": 25840, "end_ms": 27120, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那這到底是怎麼回事呢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 12, "start_ms": 27120, "end_ms": 28080, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我們可以看到", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 13, "start_ms": 28080, "end_ms": 29600, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "各個各大寬機", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 14, "start_ms": 29600, "end_ms": 31360, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實表現其實都是比較弱的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 15, "start_ms": 31360, "end_ms": 33480, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "像中正1000 國正2000", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 16, "start_ms": 33480, "end_ms": 34720, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後包括中正500", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 17, "start_ms": 34720, "end_ms": 36840, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實基本上都跌了一點幾左右", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 18, "start_ms": 36840, "end_ms": 37680, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但反過來說", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 19, "start_ms": 37680, "end_ms": 38920, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "微盤股是漲的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 20, "start_ms": 38920, "end_ms": 39960, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "全中位數是漲的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 21, "start_ms": 39960, "end_ms": 40680, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "微盤股的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 22, "start_ms": 40680, "end_ms": 42840, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實很久之前就提醒大家了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 23, "start_ms": 42840, "end_ms": 44920, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是說你會發現", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 24, "start_ms": 44920, "end_ms": 47720, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "當說整個市場的槓桿率", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 25, "start_ms": 47720, "end_ms": 48880, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "最高的一個地方", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 26, "start_ms": 48880, "end_ms": 50760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "比如說像半導體 雲期間", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 27, "start_ms": 50850, "end_ms": 51870, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者同性设备", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 28, "start_ms": 51870, "end_ms": 53670, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他们是杠杆最高的一个地方", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 29, "start_ms": 53670, "end_ms": 54750, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "出现这种类似", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 30, "start_ms": 54750, "end_ms": 56150, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因为今天又崩溃了对吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 31, "start_ms": 56150, "end_ms": 58470, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "又出现了这种崩溃的这个状况的时候", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 32, "start_ms": 58470, "end_ms": 59750, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一部分的这个量化资金", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 33, "start_ms": 59750, "end_ms": 61350, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它就会回到微盘里面去", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 34, "start_ms": 61350, "end_ms": 61830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "为什么", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 35, "start_ms": 61830, "end_ms": 64830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因为微盘里面它没有杠杆", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 36, "start_ms": 64830, "end_ms": 66230, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "微盘 而且是拥挤度", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 37, "start_ms": 66230, "end_ms": 67070, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "在今年的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 38, "start_ms": 67070, "end_ms": 69350, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "算是拥挤度最低的一个方向之一了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 39, "start_ms": 69350, "end_ms": 70590, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说在这里面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 40, "start_ms": 70590, "end_ms": 71790, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它没有杂盘力量", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 41, "start_ms": 71790, "end_ms": 72990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因为跌过一大波了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 42, "start_ms": 73020, "end_ms": 74620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说它没有什么杂判令", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 43, "start_ms": 74620, "end_ms": 77420, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是你在其他的这些东西里面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 44, "start_ms": 77420, "end_ms": 78780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就有可能是为什么呢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 45, "start_ms": 78780, "end_ms": 79980, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "有可能会被", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 46, "start_ms": 79980, "end_ms": 83260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "比如说去钢杆的一部分的资金被砸", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 47, "start_ms": 83260, "end_ms": 84420, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "哪里在去钢杆呢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 48, "start_ms": 84420, "end_ms": 85300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大家也可以看一下", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 49, "start_ms": 85300, "end_ms": 87340, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "像融资融券我们点两融前景", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 50, "start_ms": 87340, "end_ms": 89180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们可以特别明显的看得到", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 51, "start_ms": 89180, "end_ms": 91540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "近期你看从7月20日开始", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 52, "start_ms": 91540, "end_ms": 93740, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "几乎每一天的整个的融资约", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 53, "start_ms": 93740, "end_ms": 96380, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "都是在不停不停不停不停的在下滑的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 54, "start_ms": 96380, "end_ms": 98060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "而由于他们在下滑", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 55, "start_ms": 98060, "end_ms": 99460, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "跑的跌得多了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 56, "start_ms": 99460, "end_ms": 101180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "不管說是市場在漲", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 57, "start_ms": 101180, "end_ms": 102620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "反彈還是在下跌", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 58, "start_ms": 102620, "end_ms": 104780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他們都在持續的在去槓桿", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 59, "start_ms": 104780, "end_ms": 106460, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個是代表說整個市場", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 60, "start_ms": 106460, "end_ms": 109060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "正在做一個溫和的去槓桿的動作", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 61, "start_ms": 109060, "end_ms": 110340, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "而且有一些人", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 62, "start_ms": 110340, "end_ms": 111940, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "比如說因為跌得多了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 63, "start_ms": 111940, "end_ms": 113300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "有一些票", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 64, "start_ms": 113300, "end_ms": 114180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "比如說有的時候", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 65, "start_ms": 114180, "end_ms": 115220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我們不說什麼東西", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 66, "start_ms": 115220, "end_ms": 117060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我們就說就算存儲", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 67, "start_ms": 117060, "end_ms": 118020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一刀子下來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 68, "start_ms": 118020, "end_ms": 119300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個不是一點點", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 69, "start_ms": 119300, "end_ms": 120780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "要跌很多 500多塊錢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 70, "start_ms": 120780, "end_ms": 122420, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一下子跌到了300塊錢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 71, "start_ms": 122420, "end_ms": 124140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實在跌跌馬上腰斬了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 72, "start_ms": 124140, "end_ms": 124940, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "很快", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 73, "start_ms": 124940, "end_ms": 126580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個也就兩個星期左右的時間", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 74, "start_ms": 126580, "end_ms": 127780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "直接就腰斬了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 75, "start_ms": 127860, "end_ms": 130100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "对于说这种融资融券的标的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 76, "start_ms": 130100, "end_ms": 133260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他们毕竟说你带着杠杆以后", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 77, "start_ms": 133260, "end_ms": 134260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那情况就不一样了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 78, "start_ms": 134260, "end_ms": 136180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "有的人说带杠杆他有赚不一定", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 79, "start_ms": 136180, "end_ms": 137900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "有很多人的话杠杆很高", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 80, "start_ms": 137900, "end_ms": 139140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但人就不赚钱", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 81, "start_ms": 139140, "end_ms": 141860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后反而还高位界的这个东西掉下来以后", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 82, "start_ms": 141860, "end_ms": 144620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个时候他就会面临一定的这种屏藏的风险", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 83, "start_ms": 144620, "end_ms": 146580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "和你说他不屏藏", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 84, "start_ms": 146580, "end_ms": 147900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那跌得多了以后", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 85, "start_ms": 147900, "end_ms": 149100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他心里也会有恐惧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 86, "start_ms": 149100, "end_ms": 150860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "为什么有本金盔的差不多了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 87, "start_ms": 150860, "end_ms": 151940, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他也会割肉的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 88, "start_ms": 151940, "end_ms": 152540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一样的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 89, "start_ms": 152540, "end_ms": 153460, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 90, "start_ms": 153570, "end_ms": 156810, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "强如这个存储也都长成这个样子", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 91, "start_ms": 156810, "end_ms": 158890, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说我们自己也就能够知道了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 92, "start_ms": 158890, "end_ms": 162410, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "第一个 平时没有太大的这种", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 93, "start_ms": 162410, "end_ms": 164650, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是赌信的吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 94, "start_ms": 164650, "end_ms": 166170, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你赌信不要这么足的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 95, "start_ms": 166170, "end_ms": 167570, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就不要上杠杆杆", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 96, "start_ms": 167570, "end_ms": 169010, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其实A股很简单", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 97, "start_ms": 169010, "end_ms": 170170, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你不上杠杆", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 98, "start_ms": 170170, "end_ms": 172050, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "在一个不高的位置", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 99, "start_ms": 172050, "end_ms": 173330, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "估值很低的位置", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 100, "start_ms": 173330, "end_ms": 174490, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "如果去拿下", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 101, "start_ms": 174490, "end_ms": 175530, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后等等", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 102, "start_ms": 175530, "end_ms": 176490, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大概就这样子", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 103, "start_ms": 176490, "end_ms": 178490, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "A股其实要说简单就简单", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 104, "start_ms": 178490, "end_ms": 180290, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是等等的这个过程当中", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 105, "start_ms": 180290, "end_ms": 181810, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它必定是波动的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 106, "start_ms": 181760, "end_ms": 183440, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你進來以後 你說差不多", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 107, "start_ms": 183440, "end_ms": 184480, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我覺得到這裡可以了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 108, "start_ms": 184480, "end_ms": 185640, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "後面又跌了一波", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 109, "start_ms": 186340, "end_ms": 187780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個等等的過程當中", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 110, "start_ms": 187780, "end_ms": 189220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它會有贏有賺", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 111, "start_ms": 189220, "end_ms": 190460, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你可能在一段時間", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 112, "start_ms": 190460, "end_ms": 192540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你說到最後我在等等過程當中", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 113, "start_ms": 192540, "end_ms": 194380, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "等了半年等了三個月", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 114, "start_ms": 194580, "end_ms": 196260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者等了三個季度", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 115, "start_ms": 196260, "end_ms": 197500, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它都是虧損的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 116, "start_ms": 197500, "end_ms": 198820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但之後引力了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 117, "start_ms": 198820, "end_ms": 200660, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "比如說在這裡引力了10個點", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 118, "start_ms": 200660, "end_ms": 202620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你說然後把它走掉了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 119, "start_ms": 202620, "end_ms": 204780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你說在這種做法上面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 120, "start_ms": 205940, "end_ms": 206700, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 121, "start_ms": 206780, "end_ms": 208900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "論對比說銀行存款來說", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 122, "start_ms": 208900, "end_ms": 211300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實安全性要來的高得多的多", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 123, "start_ms": 211300, "end_ms": 213380, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實很非常簡單的一個活", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 124, "start_ms": 213380, "end_ms": 215180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但很多人是不願意這麼去幹的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 125, "start_ms": 215180, "end_ms": 215660, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因為為什麼", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 126, "start_ms": 215660, "end_ms": 216700, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因為那邊還在漲", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 127, "start_ms": 216700, "end_ms": 217180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那邊在衝", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 128, "start_ms": 217500, "end_ms": 218860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你看進去就能有十個點", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 129, "start_ms": 219580, "end_ms": 220300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就會有這樣子", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 130, "start_ms": 220300, "end_ms": 221620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你看這些應該怎麼做", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 131, "start_ms": 221620, "end_ms": 222780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "買了就能怎麼樣", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 132, "start_ms": 222780, "end_ms": 223900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "哪有那麼簡單的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 133, "start_ms": 223900, "end_ms": 225700, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這市場永遠不是這麼簡單的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 134, "start_ms": 225700, "end_ms": 228860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "只有這個股市是從來都沒有", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 135, "start_ms": 228860, "end_ms": 231700, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "什麼比如說高效或者怎麼樣", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 136, "start_ms": 231700, "end_ms": 234060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "專門的交進炒股票的是沒有的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 137, "start_ms": 234270, "end_ms": 236990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "專門教你怎麼去投資的 幾乎也是沒有的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 138, "start_ms": 236990, "end_ms": 239070, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "對吧 但是這個東西的門檻有很低", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 139, "start_ms": 239070, "end_ms": 241270, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "很多人一開戶就能買入賣出我會了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 140, "start_ms": 241270, "end_ms": 243670, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大概就這樣子 這個強 強者很強", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 141, "start_ms": 243670, "end_ms": 245830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個圖形可以 大概就這樣子", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 142, "start_ms": 245830, "end_ms": 249270, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以這個是作為說股市其實難做", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 143, "start_ms": 249270, "end_ms": 253790, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "包括說很多人會感覺這個投資很困難的一個原因之一", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 144, "start_ms": 253790, "end_ms": 256750, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是其實它的本質的底層邏輯就非常簡單", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 145, "start_ms": 256750, "end_ms": 258950, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "便宜的時候買 貴的時候賣掉 就這個", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 146, "start_ms": 258990, "end_ms": 260950, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其实原理其实非常简单", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 147, "start_ms": 260950, "end_ms": 261990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但很多人到最后", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 148, "start_ms": 261990, "end_ms": 264150, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "坐着坐着慢慢的这个手就偏了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 149, "start_ms": 265080, "end_ms": 267040, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "好 那么今天整个宽气回调的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 150, "start_ms": 267040, "end_ms": 268480, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大幅度回调的一个原因", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 151, "start_ms": 268560, "end_ms": 270920, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "主要还是因为说之前的一些权重", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 152, "start_ms": 271260, "end_ms": 273900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "都集中在了像这个半导体元线通行设备", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 153, "start_ms": 273900, "end_ms": 275020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "集中在这个里面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 154, "start_ms": 275020, "end_ms": 277020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因为这个预三加一二三", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 155, "start_ms": 277020, "end_ms": 278300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "三加这个东西", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 156, "start_ms": 278300, "end_ms": 280620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这之前陈也销和拜也销和", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 157, "start_ms": 280620, "end_ms": 282420, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说你现在想要指数", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 158, "start_ms": 282420, "end_ms": 284500, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "说不跌他们跌的时候你不跌", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 159, "start_ms": 284500, "end_ms": 285580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个几乎是不可能的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 160, "start_ms": 285580, "end_ms": 288300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "甚至说我们看到像这个中正一切", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 161, "start_ms": 288300, "end_ms": 289540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你现在就反过来了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 162, "start_ms": 289540, "end_ms": 291220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你这个流通市值排一排", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 163, "start_ms": 291220, "end_ms": 293100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你市值偏大的全部一塌糊涂", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 164, "start_ms": 293100, "end_ms": 294220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你什么业绩好啊", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 165, "start_ms": 294220, "end_ms": 294980, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "业绩不好啊", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 166, "start_ms": 294980, "end_ms": 297020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "什么东西出来都给你洗着花了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 167, "start_ms": 297020, "end_ms": 297820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "都给你跌", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 168, "start_ms": 297860, "end_ms": 299860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个就是去杠杆的一个状态", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 169, "start_ms": 299860, "end_ms": 301100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "反过来可能就不一样了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 170, "start_ms": 301100, "end_ms": 302660, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "反过来都还可以", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 171, "start_ms": 302660, "end_ms": 305540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这些反过来的这一块是跌得最凶的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 172, "start_ms": 305540, "end_ms": 309220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其他东西被市场的资金去红吸掉了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 173, "start_ms": 309220, "end_ms": 310820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这纯粹是资金行为", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 174, "start_ms": 310880, "end_ms": 312960, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "好多人可能說你看不一定", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 175, "start_ms": 312960, "end_ms": 314400, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他們這個票大的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 176, "start_ms": 314400, "end_ms": 315600, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他們就是業績好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 177, "start_ms": 315600, "end_ms": 317040, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他們或者說他們就是好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 178, "start_ms": 317040, "end_ms": 317600, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "沒有的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 179, "start_ms": 317600, "end_ms": 319040, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實這個裡面有很多的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 180, "start_ms": 319040, "end_ms": 320880, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "100多億的這種東西", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 181, "start_ms": 320880, "end_ms": 322880, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "有很多的其實還不錯的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 182, "start_ms": 322880, "end_ms": 324480, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是在這一輪裡面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 183, "start_ms": 324480, "end_ms": 325680, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "今年的這一輪裡面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 184, "start_ms": 325680, "end_ms": 328240, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "被白白被整個資金被紅吸了很多", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 185, "start_ms": 328240, "end_ms": 330160, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "莫名其妙的吃了一大刀子", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 186, "start_ms": 330160, "end_ms": 331440, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這種的多了去了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 187, "start_ms": 331440, "end_ms": 334240, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "好 這個上面也有很多不見了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 188, "start_ms": 334240, "end_ms": 335120, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那麼好的東西", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 189, "start_ms": 335120, "end_ms": 336880, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是今年卻漲了三五倍的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 190, "start_ms": 336880, "end_ms": 337680, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這種也有", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 191, "start_ms": 337740, "end_ms": 339020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那其實到現在的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 192, "start_ms": 339020, "end_ms": 341060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "市場如果說它要再平衡", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 193, "start_ms": 341060, "end_ms": 343180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個市值偏大的一些品種", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 194, "start_ms": 343180, "end_ms": 344500, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它就會偏低一點", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 195, "start_ms": 344500, "end_ms": 345860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就你這個市值偏大的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 196, "start_ms": 345860, "end_ms": 347220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那除非說之後", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 197, "start_ms": 347220, "end_ms": 347860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就有一些東西", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 198, "start_ms": 347860, "end_ms": 349020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但真的是非常的硬", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 199, "start_ms": 349020, "end_ms": 350500, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那它能夠稍微活下來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 200, "start_ms": 350500, "end_ms": 351740, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "如果說不是那麼硬的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 201, "start_ms": 351740, "end_ms": 352780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大概率是活不下來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 202, "start_ms": 352780, "end_ms": 353940, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "雖然說他們也做出了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 203, "start_ms": 353940, "end_ms": 356140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一定的這個拯救的一個動作", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 204, "start_ms": 356140, "end_ms": 357900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是市值最大的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 205, "start_ms": 357900, "end_ms": 358700, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我給你紅一紅", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 206, "start_ms": 358700, "end_ms": 361300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是基本上難言褪世", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 207, "start_ms": 361300, "end_ms": 362900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你反過來的話那就不一樣了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 208, "start_ms": 362900, "end_ms": 364460, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你反過來還可以", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 209, "start_ms": 364450, "end_ms": 365890, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "對吧 發現是這樣子", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 210, "start_ms": 365890, "end_ms": 369370, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說現在不能說是回到了一個老燈的時代", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 211, "start_ms": 369370, "end_ms": 370970, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "而是說是偏大的品種", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 212, "start_ms": 370970, "end_ms": 374850, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它反而是在現在的話是一個負向的一個因子", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 213, "start_ms": 374850, "end_ms": 376490, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你試試偏小的 反而會好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 214, "start_ms": 376490, "end_ms": 378290, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那原理就是告訴大家的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 215, "start_ms": 378290, "end_ms": 380330, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "資金會去這個微盤股", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 216, "start_ms": 380330, "end_ms": 381210, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個是一塊", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 217, "start_ms": 381210, "end_ms": 382250, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後另外一個的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 218, "start_ms": 382250, "end_ms": 384330, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我們看一下這個海外", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 219, "start_ms": 384510, "end_ms": 388910, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因為昨天的話美國是公佈了CPI的數據", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 220, "start_ms": 388910, "end_ms": 390270, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它環比是一個負增長", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 221, "start_ms": 390270, "end_ms": 391870, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說很多人會覺得說", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 222, "start_ms": 391870, "end_ms": 393310, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你看這個環比負增長了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 223, "start_ms": 393310, "end_ms": 395310, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說它這個就應該大漲了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 224, "start_ms": 395310, "end_ms": 396270, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你只要去看", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 225, "start_ms": 396270, "end_ms": 398150, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實非常簡單 你只要去看黃金", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 226, "start_ms": 398150, "end_ms": 400830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "黃金其實在這裡基本上沒有什麼大的反應", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 227, "start_ms": 400830, "end_ms": 401910, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "為什麼會這樣子", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 228, "start_ms": 401910, "end_ms": 402990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實原因很簡單", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 229, "start_ms": 402990, "end_ms": 405710, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因為CPI它是一個智候指標", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 230, "start_ms": 405710, "end_ms": 406910, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "之前的話油價", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 231, "start_ms": 406910, "end_ms": 408950, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因為在這裡掉了一大波了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 232, "start_ms": 408950, "end_ms": 410830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說CPI在這裡", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 233, "start_ms": 410830, "end_ms": 413230, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它出現一個負增長挺正常的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 234, "start_ms": 413310, "end_ms": 415470, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是我們不是環比的一個負增長", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 235, "start_ms": 415470, "end_ms": 416270, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "挺正常的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 236, "start_ms": 416270, "end_ms": 417950, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因為油價是掉下來了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 237, "start_ms": 417950, "end_ms": 420270, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "而且掉了很多這些數據都能夠看得到", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 238, "start_ms": 420270, "end_ms": 423790, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是論說現在的最新的數據要去看什麼呢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 239, "start_ms": 423790, "end_ms": 424670, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "還是看油價", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 240, "start_ms": 424670, "end_ms": 426350, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "油價它是一個鮮性指標", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 241, "start_ms": 426350, "end_ms": 427470, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "油價如果跑上來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 242, "start_ms": 427470, "end_ms": 429550, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "現在還能算勉強85左右", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 243, "start_ms": 429550, "end_ms": 430990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "如果你有跑到90億上籃", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 244, "start_ms": 430990, "end_ms": 432670, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "對整個市場的衝擊", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 245, "start_ms": 432670, "end_ms": 434510, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "實質性的衝擊又回來了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 246, "start_ms": 434510, "end_ms": 436110, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說這裡的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 247, "start_ms": 436110, "end_ms": 437790, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你現在看到可能說感覺", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 248, "start_ms": 437790, "end_ms": 439550, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "喔 CPI還可以對吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 249, "start_ms": 439550, "end_ms": 441870, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "加息預期就沒了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 250, "start_ms": 441920, "end_ms": 443560, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "今年加息区就没了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 251, "start_ms": 443560, "end_ms": 445760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是如果说等到油价又跑上去了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 252, "start_ms": 445760, "end_ms": 447840, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你CPOE CPI又上来了 对吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 253, "start_ms": 447840, "end_ms": 448720, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "年薪又很足", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 254, "start_ms": 448720, "end_ms": 451280, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其实它本质是反映的是一个油价", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 255, "start_ms": 451280, "end_ms": 453640, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其他东西其实也就一般性了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 256, "start_ms": 453640, "end_ms": 455000, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说在这个角度上面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 257, "start_ms": 455000, "end_ms": 455880, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们去看的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 258, "start_ms": 455880, "end_ms": 458360, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "黄金在这里它暂时来说", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 259, "start_ms": 458360, "end_ms": 459400, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们还没有看到说", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 260, "start_ms": 459400, "end_ms": 461440, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它有特别明显的这个", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 261, "start_ms": 461440, "end_ms": 463840, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "上升的這種真正去上升的一個動能", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 262, "start_ms": 463840, "end_ms": 465480, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就特別在加息預期下", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 263, "start_ms": 465480, "end_ms": 467280, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "什麼時候它要變成降息預期了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 264, "start_ms": 467280, "end_ms": 468240, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那就來了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 265, "start_ms": 468240, "end_ms": 470520, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者什麼時候你看到美國的經濟", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 266, "start_ms": 470520, "end_ms": 471920, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "確確實實就業", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 267, "start_ms": 471920, "end_ms": 474760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者說他們的這個分辨就業數據", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 268, "start_ms": 474760, "end_ms": 476960, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "出現一個明顯的一個下滑了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 269, "start_ms": 476960, "end_ms": 478760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那個時候黃金來了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 270, "start_ms": 478760, "end_ms": 481200, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它反映的是一個摔退的一個邏輯", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 271, "start_ms": 481200, "end_ms": 483720, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說如果說你在那邊要準備去加息", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 272, "start_ms": 483720, "end_ms": 485920, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "黃金這個就不大容易漲的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 273, "start_ms": 485920, "end_ms": 487440, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "當然現在你要跌到哪裡去", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 274, "start_ms": 487440, "end_ms": 488320, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "也跌不到哪裡去了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 275, "start_ms": 488320, "end_ms": 490160, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "也就這個價格了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 276, "start_ms": 490380, "end_ms": 491620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "好 那麼這個是一個", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 277, "start_ms": 491620, "end_ms": 493780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後另外一個很多人說韓國股市", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 278, "start_ms": 493780, "end_ms": 496580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "韓國股市這個動作就跟大家講過", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 279, "start_ms": 496580, "end_ms": 499380, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個動作其實它就是2015年的中國", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 280, "start_ms": 499380, "end_ms": 501540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實它兩者是完全一模一樣的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 281, "start_ms": 501540, "end_ms": 503100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "沒有任何一點點的差別", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 282, "start_ms": 503100, "end_ms": 504100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我們可以把它框過來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 283, "start_ms": 504100, "end_ms": 505620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你就能夠看得出來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 284, "start_ms": 505980, "end_ms": 507580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "好 我來給大家對比一下", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 285, "start_ms": 507580, "end_ms": 508900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "用兩個軟件給大家對比一下", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 286, "start_ms": 508900, "end_ms": 511820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你就會發現它幾乎在這個幾個點上", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 287, "start_ms": 511820, "end_ms": 513020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "長的是一模一樣的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 288, "start_ms": 513020, "end_ms": 514419, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這裡是一模一樣的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 289, "start_ms": 514700, "end_ms": 515460, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後拉起來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 290, "start_ms": 515460, "end_ms": 516179, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後拉起來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 291, "start_ms": 516179, "end_ms": 517020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後震盪", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 292, "start_ms": 517070, "end_ms": 518929, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後震盪一模一樣的一個動作", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 293, "start_ms": 518929, "end_ms": 520770, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後快速拉伸", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 294, "start_ms": 520770, "end_ms": 522610, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後一 二 三", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 295, "start_ms": 522929, "end_ms": 524690, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一 二 三一模一樣的動作", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 296, "start_ms": 524690, "end_ms": 526050, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "完全意志的一個動作", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 297, "start_ms": 526050, "end_ms": 527170, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說這一刀", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 298, "start_ms": 527170, "end_ms": 528970, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "現在韓國他們遇到的這一刀", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 299, "start_ms": 528970, "end_ms": 530650, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實就相當於我們2015年", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 300, "start_ms": 530650, "end_ms": 533290, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "當時我們稱之為叫古災1.0的這一段", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 301, "start_ms": 533290, "end_ms": 535810, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後它也遇到了和我們相似的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 302, "start_ms": 535810, "end_ms": 537130, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "在同樣一個點", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 303, "start_ms": 537130, "end_ms": 539450, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "在這個點上出現了一個十字星", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 304, "start_ms": 539450, "end_ms": 540890, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後好像是直跌了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 305, "start_ms": 540890, "end_ms": 542970, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後之後就是一個快速的反彈", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 306, "start_ms": 542970, "end_ms": 544730, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "連續一到兩天的一個快速反彈", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 307, "start_ms": 544800, "end_ms": 546200, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一幕一样的一个指数", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 308, "start_ms": 546200, "end_ms": 547080, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个点上的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 309, "start_ms": 547080, "end_ms": 548720, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "当时的话我们也就事", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 310, "start_ms": 548720, "end_ms": 551400, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "当时国家队出来就事什么的好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 311, "start_ms": 551400, "end_ms": 553160, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "到最后出现反弹了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 312, "start_ms": 553160, "end_ms": 554320, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这里的话也是类似", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 313, "start_ms": 554320, "end_ms": 555760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "比如说禁止错空什么", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 314, "start_ms": 555760, "end_ms": 558440, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是它的背景是完全一幕一样的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 315, "start_ms": 558440, "end_ms": 559120, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "背景是什么呢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 316, "start_ms": 559120, "end_ms": 559920, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "去杠杆", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 317, "start_ms": 559920, "end_ms": 561480, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就韩国现在也在去杠杆", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 318, "start_ms": 561480, "end_ms": 563120, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因为它要把保证金起高五倍", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 319, "start_ms": 563120, "end_ms": 564480, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说这样子的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 320, "start_ms": 564670, "end_ms": 566270, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "如果說他們去槓桿", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 321, "start_ms": 566270, "end_ms": 567310, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "和當15年的時候", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 322, "start_ms": 567310, "end_ms": 569110, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "當時一樣做一模一樣的動作的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 323, "start_ms": 569110, "end_ms": 570030, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "現在後面的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 324, "start_ms": 570030, "end_ms": 570990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那你就很簡單", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 325, "start_ms": 570990, "end_ms": 573590, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你直接去參考15年的A股的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 326, "start_ms": 573590, "end_ms": 574590, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "後面的一個行情", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 327, "start_ms": 574590, "end_ms": 576430, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "基本上你能夠去確定", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 328, "start_ms": 576430, "end_ms": 578430, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "韓國大概後面會怎麼走", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 329, "start_ms": 578430, "end_ms": 579750, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你就把它移到這裡", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 330, "start_ms": 579750, "end_ms": 580710, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你就已經看到了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 331, "start_ms": 580710, "end_ms": 581590, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "後面的一個走法", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 332, "start_ms": 581590, "end_ms": 582750, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "後面走法是什麼呢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 333, "start_ms": 582750, "end_ms": 584670, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "形成這麼一個三角形", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 334, "start_ms": 584670, "end_ms": 585670, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說在這裡", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 335, "start_ms": 585670, "end_ms": 587190, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "形成這麼一個三角形", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 336, "start_ms": 587190, "end_ms": 588190, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後走到這裡以後", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 337, "start_ms": 588190, "end_ms": 590150, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "框又是第二道子又來了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 338, "start_ms": 590150, "end_ms": 591470, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "第二道子來了以後", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 339, "start_ms": 591470, "end_ms": 592350, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它會震到", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 340, "start_ms": 592340, "end_ms": 593620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "會欺問一段時間", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 341, "start_ms": 593620, "end_ms": 594500, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "到這裡的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 342, "start_ms": 594500, "end_ms": 595660, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "要到27年的下半年", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 343, "start_ms": 595660, "end_ms": 597300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者說在某個時間點", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 344, "start_ms": 597300, "end_ms": 598940, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它又會還會有一次回落", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 345, "start_ms": 598940, "end_ms": 599820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "再有一次回落", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 346, "start_ms": 599820, "end_ms": 601060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大概率是因為", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 347, "start_ms": 601060, "end_ms": 602140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "內存的價格", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 348, "start_ms": 602140, "end_ms": 603340, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "開始出現鬆動", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 349, "start_ms": 603340, "end_ms": 604420, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那個時候", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 350, "start_ms": 604420, "end_ms": 606220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "整個市場它會持續的下跌", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 351, "start_ms": 606220, "end_ms": 606860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "持續的下跌", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 352, "start_ms": 606860, "end_ms": 608020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你不要以為不會跌", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 353, "start_ms": 608020, "end_ms": 609540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你現在的那個", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 354, "start_ms": 609540, "end_ms": 610300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "都是", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 355, "start_ms": 610300, "end_ms": 611620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個指數是假的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 356, "start_ms": 611620, "end_ms": 612820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它其實反彈到這裡", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 357, "start_ms": 612820, "end_ms": 613620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就開始跌了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 358, "start_ms": 613620, "end_ms": 615380, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就其實真實的是這麼走的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 359, "start_ms": 615890, "end_ms": 619210, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後所以說包括說韓國指數", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 360, "start_ms": 619210, "end_ms": 621730, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實最終的一個結果都是差不多的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 361, "start_ms": 621730, "end_ms": 623130, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一旦陷入到價格站", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 362, "start_ms": 623130, "end_ms": 625210, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者說那時候價格開始滑落", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 363, "start_ms": 625210, "end_ms": 625810, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者怎麼樣", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 364, "start_ms": 625810, "end_ms": 626930, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那所有的這些東西", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 365, "start_ms": 626930, "end_ms": 628690, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你所謂看到的那些估值", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 366, "start_ms": 628690, "end_ms": 634090, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那些站在這個山巔的那些東西", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 367, "start_ms": 634090, "end_ms": 635970, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "到最後可能都是泡影", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 368, "start_ms": 635970, "end_ms": 638090, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說自己有的時候心裡面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 369, "start_ms": 638090, "end_ms": 639690, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一定要非常清晰的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 370, "start_ms": 639660, "end_ms": 641620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "能夠明白這一點", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 371, "start_ms": 641620, "end_ms": 643220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以我們看到了韓國旨說", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 372, "start_ms": 643220, "end_ms": 644660, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我們也就能知道說", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 373, "start_ms": 644660, "end_ms": 645820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "對於我們這邊來說", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 374, "start_ms": 645820, "end_ms": 647580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "說判道題為什麼還要DL", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 375, "start_ms": 647580, "end_ms": 649060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者怎麼樣子一樣的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 376, "start_ms": 649060, "end_ms": 650300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它就是去槓桿", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 377, "start_ms": 650300, "end_ms": 651420, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一樣也是去槓桿", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 378, "start_ms": 651420, "end_ms": 652260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "槓桿太高了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 379, "start_ms": 652260, "end_ms": 653700, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你在加速段裡面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 380, "start_ms": 653700, "end_ms": 654900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "既然加速段裡面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 381, "start_ms": 654900, "end_ms": 655940, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你不在裡面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 382, "start_ms": 655940, "end_ms": 657540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你既然說錯過了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 383, "start_ms": 657540, "end_ms": 658340, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "很多人錯過了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 384, "start_ms": 658340, "end_ms": 659220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我就怕錯過", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 385, "start_ms": 659220, "end_ms": 660220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就要怎麼樣子", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 386, "start_ms": 660220, "end_ms": 661260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就怎麼樣", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 387, "start_ms": 661260, "end_ms": 662580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "錯過了就錯過了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 388, "start_ms": 662580, "end_ms": 663300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我還是說了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 389, "start_ms": 663300, "end_ms": 665260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你這個一輩子錯過的女神多了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 390, "start_ms": 665260, "end_ms": 666100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "去了那錯過了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 391, "start_ms": 666100, "end_ms": 667500, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那又怎麼樣呢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 392, "start_ms": 667500, "end_ms": 668260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "對吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 393, "start_ms": 669310, "end_ms": 672910, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "對吧 所謂吧 都要幹哪 無所謂了 對不對", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 394, "start_ms": 672910, "end_ms": 676150, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就這麼過去吧 就是以後之後還有機會", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 395, "start_ms": 676150, "end_ms": 677750, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我也跟大家講了 在這個裡面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 396, "start_ms": 677750, "end_ms": 680550, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實慢慢的你會發現一些無人注意的角落", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 397, "start_ms": 680550, "end_ms": 682430, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它會出現一些機會", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 398, "start_ms": 682430, "end_ms": 684990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你會發現今天醫藥表現依舊非常不錯", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 399, "start_ms": 684990, "end_ms": 688750, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "沒錯吧 是吧 你可以看到你說強一點的大票", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 400, "start_ms": 688750, "end_ms": 690830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "當說耀明 凱萊茵 對吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 401, "start_ms": 690830, "end_ms": 693390, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那不是人就是凱琳掌聽把凱琳彈性大", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 402, "start_ms": 693390, "end_ms": 695030, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "耀明的彈性稍微小一點", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 403, "start_ms": 695100, "end_ms": 698900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "对吧 然后其他的一些 包括说一些卖铲子的一些股票啊", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 404, "start_ms": 698900, "end_ms": 702140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后包括说像这个", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 405, "start_ms": 703120, "end_ms": 706000, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大家講的像這個成都 對吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 406, "start_ms": 706000, "end_ms": 707280, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個慢慢的也都走上來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 407, "start_ms": 707280, "end_ms": 709720, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這裡的話 有一點點小小的風險", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 408, "start_ms": 709720, "end_ms": 711440, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因為它這根K線不純", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 409, "start_ms": 711440, "end_ms": 713280, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "有一半上陰線 一半下陰線", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 410, "start_ms": 713280, "end_ms": 714400, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後又是帶量的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 411, "start_ms": 714400, "end_ms": 715520, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "不帶量 沒關係", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 412, "start_ms": 715520, "end_ms": 718640, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "帶量的話 這裡它是有這種正當的一個需求的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 413, "start_ms": 718640, "end_ms": 719520, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個是要小心的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 414, "start_ms": 719520, "end_ms": 722120, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因為這個點上畢竟說遇到的是一個壓力", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 415, "start_ms": 722120, "end_ms": 723560, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個壓力源自於說", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 416, "start_ms": 723560, "end_ms": 725160, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這邊的一個叫陰陽木碑", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 417, "start_ms": 725160, "end_ms": 727240, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一個陰險一個陰險 陰陽木碑", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 418, "start_ms": 727240, "end_ms": 728760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "剛好就在這裡", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 419, "start_ms": 728760, "end_ms": 730200, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說這個又是個大量", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 420, "start_ms": 731330, "end_ms": 732610, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "如果没有量就好一点", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 421, "start_ms": 732610, "end_ms": 733730, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因为这个燕阳墨被掐好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 422, "start_ms": 733730, "end_ms": 734410, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "亮亮很大", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 423, "start_ms": 734410, "end_ms": 736450, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说这个点正常是一个洗盘点", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 424, "start_ms": 736450, "end_ms": 737010, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "自己注意", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 425, "start_ms": 737010, "end_ms": 738210, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "如果洗一洗的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 426, "start_ms": 738210, "end_ms": 739450, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这里它又是一个买点", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 427, "start_ms": 739450, "end_ms": 741250, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后买点可能在这个附近", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 428, "start_ms": 741250, "end_ms": 742530, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "可能不会掉到这么深", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 429, "start_ms": 742530, "end_ms": 744530, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后之后它又会往上走", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 430, "start_ms": 744530, "end_ms": 745610, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这种概率是比较高", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 431, "start_ms": 745610, "end_ms": 747170, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "当然这个肯定不是推荐", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 432, "start_ms": 747170, "end_ms": 749290, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一定要注意", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 433, "start_ms": 749290, "end_ms": 749530, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 434, "start_ms": 749530, "end_ms": 751810, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后我们来看一下红冠数据", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 435, "start_ms": 751980, "end_ms": 755820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "奧吉都的整个经济数据在这边是完全出来了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 436, "start_ms": 755820, "end_ms": 758140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是现在经济数据我们主要去看几个点", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 437, "start_ms": 758140, "end_ms": 760060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就有很多朋友比如说", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 438, "start_ms": 760060, "end_ms": 762540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "可能有一些东西是不大明白的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 439, "start_ms": 762540, "end_ms": 763820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "什么跟大家稍微解释一下吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 440, "start_ms": 763820, "end_ms": 764740, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是这里面的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 441, "start_ms": 764740, "end_ms": 768060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "第一个就是说我们看到这个GDP的民意帧数是5.9", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 442, "start_ms": 768060, "end_ms": 769500, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个民意帧数其实可以", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 443, "start_ms": 769500, "end_ms": 771260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "实际帧数是4.3", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 444, "start_ms": 771260, "end_ms": 773660, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这其实论奧吉都的话其实", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 445, "start_ms": 774460, "end_ms": 777060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "還有肯大的一個提升的空間是4.3", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 446, "start_ms": 777060, "end_ms": 778140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這裡面是什麼意思呢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 447, "start_ms": 778140, "end_ms": 779340, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是你可以很簡單", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 448, "start_ms": 779340, "end_ms": 780420, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你把這個民意增速", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 449, "start_ms": 780420, "end_ms": 783140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "民意增速其實它就是算上通帳", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 450, "start_ms": 783140, "end_ms": 785060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是你物價的增長我算進去", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 451, "start_ms": 785060, "end_ms": 786260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那就是5.9", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 452, "start_ms": 786260, "end_ms": 788900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那如果不算的話那就是4.3", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 453, "start_ms": 788900, "end_ms": 791580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那其實特別是在這個今年的一個上半年", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 454, "start_ms": 791580, "end_ms": 793940, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實出現了一個非常明顯的輸入性通帳", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 455, "start_ms": 793940, "end_ms": 795580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這通帳來自於說海峽的封閉", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 456, "start_ms": 795580, "end_ms": 797380, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "油價上漲各種各樣的原因", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 457, "start_ms": 797380, "end_ms": 799700, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說你可以把這個5.9去減4.3", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 458, "start_ms": 799700, "end_ms": 802420, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那大概等於1.61.6", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 459, "start_ms": 803680, "end_ms": 806920, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個GDP的一個叫評鑑指數", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 460, "start_ms": 806920, "end_ms": 809680, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是那麼這個評鑑指數它的一個作用", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 461, "start_ms": 809680, "end_ms": 810600, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實是什麼東西呢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 462, "start_ms": 810600, "end_ms": 813240, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它其實它就是告訴你說", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 463, "start_ms": 813240, "end_ms": 815240, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "在這個季度的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 464, "start_ms": 815240, "end_ms": 818240, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "意思就是如果你是生產一個麵包", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 465, "start_ms": 818240, "end_ms": 820600, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一個麵包如果說是100塊錢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 466, "start_ms": 820600, "end_ms": 822200, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "比如一箱麵包100塊錢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 467, "start_ms": 822200, "end_ms": 825000, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "現在變成101塊6毛", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 468, "start_ms": 825000, "end_ms": 826680, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那就長了1.6%", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 469, "start_ms": 826680, "end_ms": 827320, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "很多人一看", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 470, "start_ms": 827320, "end_ms": 828240, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我這數據起來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 471, "start_ms": 828240, "end_ms": 830800, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但不是說我們這邊就沒有通縮了 是吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 472, "start_ms": 830820, "end_ms": 833220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那当然了 我从来没说过我们这边有通缩", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 473, "start_ms": 833220, "end_ms": 834860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是都是海外在胡说八道", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 474, "start_ms": 834860, "end_ms": 835620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "说我们有通缩", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 475, "start_ms": 835620, "end_ms": 837020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那其实是看这个数据", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 476, "start_ms": 837020, "end_ms": 839380, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "去看通缩完全是不匹配的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 477, "start_ms": 839380, "end_ms": 839900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因为为什么", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 478, "start_ms": 839900, "end_ms": 840900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因为在这个里面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 479, "start_ms": 840900, "end_ms": 843100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它包含了很多部分的一个内容", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 480, "start_ms": 843100, "end_ms": 844260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因为它是GDP", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 481, "start_ms": 844260, "end_ms": 845620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说一部分的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 482, "start_ms": 845620, "end_ms": 846740, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你也可以把它理解成", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 483, "start_ms": 846740, "end_ms": 849020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它又是包含了一部分CPI的内容", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 484, "start_ms": 849020, "end_ms": 851020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "又包含了一部分PPI的内容", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 485, "start_ms": 851020, "end_ms": 853020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "又包含了一部分的政府投资", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 486, "start_ms": 853020, "end_ms": 854660, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这几块全部加在一起", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 487, "start_ms": 854660, "end_ms": 856860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说你和你真实体感可能不大", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 488, "start_ms": 856860, "end_ms": 857820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你说真实体感不对", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 489, "start_ms": 857820, "end_ms": 858820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我这边含", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 490, "start_ms": 858850, "end_ms": 860170, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個價格都賣不上去", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 491, "start_ms": 860170, "end_ms": 862090, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那其實它更多的一個點", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 492, "start_ms": 862090, "end_ms": 863690, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是你生產出來價格貴的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 493, "start_ms": 863690, "end_ms": 864610, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它這個也會貴", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 494, "start_ms": 864610, "end_ms": 866330, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說是這麼回事", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 495, "start_ms": 866330, "end_ms": 867570, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "當然你也可以理解說", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 496, "start_ms": 867570, "end_ms": 869090, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "哎 你說我收入不高", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 497, "start_ms": 869090, "end_ms": 870130, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者收入變低了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 498, "start_ms": 870130, "end_ms": 873130, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是 但是它的物價高了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 499, "start_ms": 873120, "end_ms": 875640, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實因為它輸入信通障來的時候", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 500, "start_ms": 875640, "end_ms": 876960, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "也會出現這種情況", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 501, "start_ms": 876960, "end_ms": 879040, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這一點大家也要諒解", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 502, "start_ms": 879040, "end_ms": 880280, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "能夠明白這一點", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 503, "start_ms": 880280, "end_ms": 881920, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "另外一個工業產能利用率的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 504, "start_ms": 881920, "end_ms": 883440, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "如果說我們去看絕對值的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 505, "start_ms": 883440, "end_ms": 885040, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "從去年的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 506, "start_ms": 885040, "end_ms": 886880, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一路過來到現在的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 507, "start_ms": 886880, "end_ms": 888560, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個季度其實是偏弱的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 508, "start_ms": 888560, "end_ms": 891080, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "而且它是有一定的趨勢性偏弱的這種情況", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 509, "start_ms": 891080, "end_ms": 892160, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "24年的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 510, "start_ms": 892180, "end_ms": 895180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "年底的时候其实看上去这个数据还能说勉强的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 511, "start_ms": 895180, "end_ms": 897300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们现在看到这个7474", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 512, "start_ms": 897300, "end_ms": 898860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "慢慢 慢慢 慢慢73", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 513, "start_ms": 898860, "end_ms": 900820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个产能利用率越来越低", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 514, "start_ms": 900820, "end_ms": 903260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "也就代表说它有一定的这种", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 515, "start_ms": 903260, "end_ms": 905380, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "会不会有一定的产能过剩的这种状况", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 516, "start_ms": 905380, "end_ms": 906300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者说需求不足", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 517, "start_ms": 906300, "end_ms": 907140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "要么就产能过剩", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 518, "start_ms": 907140, "end_ms": 908060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "要么就需求不足", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 519, "start_ms": 908060, "end_ms": 908500, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "对吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 520, "start_ms": 908500, "end_ms": 909580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "产能利用率才会不高", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 521, "start_ms": 909580, "end_ms": 910860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你机器开不了这么多", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 522, "start_ms": 910860, "end_ms": 911740, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你机器全开出去", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 523, "start_ms": 911740, "end_ms": 912540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "东西要么不出去", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 524, "start_ms": 912540, "end_ms": 914140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "对吧 大概是这个意思", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 525, "start_ms": 914140, "end_ms": 917500, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后我们再去看这个贡献比较大的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 526, "start_ms": 917500, "end_ms": 918660, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "工业增加值是", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 527, "start_ms": 918660, "end_ms": 919580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "调查上个月的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 528, "start_ms": 919580, "end_ms": 920780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大概是0.8左右", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 529, "start_ms": 920780, "end_ms": 922620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那确实这个数字是不错的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 530, "start_ms": 922620, "end_ms": 925180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是这个里面形成的是冰火两重天", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 531, "start_ms": 925180, "end_ms": 927700, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "现在这种什么型分化是不能说", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 532, "start_ms": 927700, "end_ms": 928900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是我们可以说", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 533, "start_ms": 928900, "end_ms": 930220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个冰火两重天", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 534, "start_ms": 930220, "end_ms": 931900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "哪里冰火 哪里有冰 哪里有火", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 535, "start_ms": 931900, "end_ms": 933580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "火的地方主要是在于", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 536, "start_ms": 933580, "end_ms": 935060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "高薪技术的一个制造业", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 537, "start_ms": 935060, "end_ms": 937220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那这个是我们向科技转型的一个", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 538, "start_ms": 937220, "end_ms": 938380, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "重要的一个", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 539, "start_ms": 938400, "end_ms": 940520, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一个方向应该来说表现是非常不错的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 540, "start_ms": 940520, "end_ms": 941840, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "还有一部分是公共事业", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 541, "start_ms": 941840, "end_ms": 943080, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "公共事业表现非常好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 542, "start_ms": 943080, "end_ms": 944760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其实在这个两个月当中", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 543, "start_ms": 945280, "end_ms": 947360, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那当然我们也不希望他们表现很好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 544, "start_ms": 947360, "end_ms": 949920, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但如果高技术制造业表现好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 545, "start_ms": 949920, "end_ms": 950960, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们觉得还是好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 546, "start_ms": 950960, "end_ms": 953000, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "是甚至说我们在这里求是", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 547, "start_ms": 953000, "end_ms": 955760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们在今天早上发现了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 548, "start_ms": 955760, "end_ms": 958640, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "有一个叫打好科技强国工建站", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 549, "start_ms": 958640, "end_ms": 959440, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 550, "start_ms": 959390, "end_ms": 961430, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這種東西 你去讀這種文章", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 551, "start_ms": 961430, "end_ms": 963550, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一般來說的話 第一個就是讀標題", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 552, "start_ms": 963550, "end_ms": 965990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "標題的話 如果是攻堅戰的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 553, "start_ms": 965990, "end_ms": 967070, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "如果考慮攻堅戰", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 554, "start_ms": 967070, "end_ms": 970350, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這是一個幾乎是接近於最高的一個", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 555, "start_ms": 970350, "end_ms": 973310, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這種名字的一種表達方式", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 556, "start_ms": 973310, "end_ms": 977190, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說對於這個科技的一個突破", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 557, "start_ms": 977190, "end_ms": 981430, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者說中美之間的一個科技爭霸", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 558, "start_ms": 981380, "end_ms": 984140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "在这里我们认为说肯定是还没有结束的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 559, "start_ms": 984140, "end_ms": 986180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "虽然说最近整个市场是在去杠杆", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 560, "start_ms": 986180, "end_ms": 987580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "在去的差不多了以后", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 561, "start_ms": 987580, "end_ms": 989900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "还陆陆续续科技他们又会回归的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 562, "start_ms": 989900, "end_ms": 991820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "也就是说到之后你会看到", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 563, "start_ms": 991820, "end_ms": 992820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "科技会有一个五浪", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 564, "start_ms": 992820, "end_ms": 994260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "现在是四浪的补碟", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 565, "start_ms": 994260, "end_ms": 996580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就你会看到他们本来就涨的太多了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 566, "start_ms": 996580, "end_ms": 997580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说跌一点", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 567, "start_ms": 997580, "end_ms": 999260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "跌完以后之后又会回来的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 568, "start_ms": 999260, "end_ms": 1000100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "现在是什么", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 569, "start_ms": 1000100, "end_ms": 1002900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "弓箭站你去看它的一个提文就知道了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 570, "start_ms": 1002900, "end_ms": 1005020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "当然现在矛盾点也有", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 571, "start_ms": 1005020, "end_ms": 1007220, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "也不是说没有矛盾点", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 572, "start_ms": 1007220, "end_ms": 1010300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以在这个点上科技以后", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 573, "start_ms": 1010300, "end_ms": 1012780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "很可能还会比较好 现在的景量放放", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 574, "start_ms": 1012780, "end_ms": 1015460, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "还不如说我们的苦命人组合", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 575, "start_ms": 1015460, "end_ms": 1017260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "虽然说我们经常说苦命人 苦命人", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 576, "start_ms": 1017260, "end_ms": 1018820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "怕高都是苦命人 对吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 577, "start_ms": 1018820, "end_ms": 1020140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但你仔细想一想说", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 578, "start_ms": 1020140, "end_ms": 1022140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "有的朋友说证券也没涨多少", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 579, "start_ms": 1022140, "end_ms": 1024099, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "证券是在这里的话都没跌", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 580, "start_ms": 1024099, "end_ms": 1027609, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "6月份过来 一路过来它没有跌", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 581, "start_ms": 1027609, "end_ms": 1029650, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "理解吧 你换一个东西就不一样了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 582, "start_ms": 1029650, "end_ms": 1030650, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "换一个东西你搞不好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 583, "start_ms": 1030650, "end_ms": 1031650, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个东西是跌的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 584, "start_ms": 1031650, "end_ms": 1032810, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你到6月份过来", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 585, "start_ms": 1032810, "end_ms": 1034329, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一路过来 西里花拉是跌的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 586, "start_ms": 1034329, "end_ms": 1035609, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个都是跌的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 587, "start_ms": 1035609, "end_ms": 1036849, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你换一个东西是跌的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 588, "start_ms": 1036849, "end_ms": 1038250, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个东西还是涨的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 589, "start_ms": 1038250, "end_ms": 1040810, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "不错了 这其实已经很不错了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 590, "start_ms": 1040690, "end_ms": 1043329, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "更加不要说是医药了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 591, "start_ms": 1043329, "end_ms": 1044569, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "医药的话那就更强了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 592, "start_ms": 1044569, "end_ms": 1045530, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "6月份过来的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 593, "start_ms": 1045530, "end_ms": 1046890, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一路过来都是上涨的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 594, "start_ms": 1046890, "end_ms": 1048569, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个苦命人组合是相当好的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 595, "start_ms": 1048569, "end_ms": 1049650, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "怕高都是苦命人", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 596, "start_ms": 1049650, "end_ms": 1051250, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那我们就既然是苦命人", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 597, "start_ms": 1051250, "end_ms": 1052570, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们一样有苦命人的路", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 598, "start_ms": 1052570, "end_ms": 1053170, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "对吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 599, "start_ms": 1053630, "end_ms": 1055190, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们不是天命人", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 600, "start_ms": 1055550, "end_ms": 1056870, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们是苦命人", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 601, "start_ms": 1056870, "end_ms": 1059590, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但苦命人我们也能找到苦命人生存之道", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 602, "start_ms": 1060470, "end_ms": 1061590, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "好 然后继续来看", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 603, "start_ms": 1061590, "end_ms": 1063350, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "相对来说偏弱一点的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 604, "start_ms": 1063350, "end_ms": 1065310, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "主要是固定资产的投资", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 605, "start_ms": 1065310, "end_ms": 1067270, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个状态应该来说", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 606, "start_ms": 1067270, "end_ms": 1069230, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "可提升的空间是相当的大", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 607, "start_ms": 1069180, "end_ms": 1072260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因为之前的话应该来说还算是去年还算是个政治", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 608, "start_ms": 1072260, "end_ms": 1074580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "现在的话是一个巨大的一个复制", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 609, "start_ms": 1074580, "end_ms": 1076020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "而且这复制非常大", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 610, "start_ms": 1076020, "end_ms": 1079900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "也就代表说未来我们能在这块发力的可能性", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 611, "start_ms": 1079900, "end_ms": 1081100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "是变得越来越大了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 612, "start_ms": 1081100, "end_ms": 1084460, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这里面包括了明年投资制造业和房地产", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 613, "start_ms": 1084460, "end_ms": 1086140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "状况房地产我们就不说了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 614, "start_ms": 1086140, "end_ms": 1087820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "既然说这个是老动能", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 615, "start_ms": 1087820, "end_ms": 1088940, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "可能说要抛弃它", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 616, "start_ms": 1088940, "end_ms": 1091060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那么我们暂时来说的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 617, "start_ms": 1091060, "end_ms": 1092420, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们还是培育新动能为主", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 618, "start_ms": 1092420, "end_ms": 1093300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个无所谓的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 619, "start_ms": 1093300, "end_ms": 1093660, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "对吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 620, "start_ms": 1093660, "end_ms": 1094780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但其他东西的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 621, "start_ms": 1094780, "end_ms": 1097260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "投资还是有很大的一个提升内空间的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 622, "start_ms": 1097630, "end_ms": 1099470, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后另外一个摄灵 很多人一看", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 623, "start_ms": 1099470, "end_ms": 1101190, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "呦 这次摄灵可以的 对吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 624, "start_ms": 1101190, "end_ms": 1102670, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "没想到你老灯站起来了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 625, "start_ms": 1102670, "end_ms": 1104590, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这边这次摄灵的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 626, "start_ms": 1104590, "end_ms": 1107070, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "在6月份的一个当月铜壁的话是回真了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 627, "start_ms": 1107070, "end_ms": 1107870, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "到了1.0了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 628, "start_ms": 1107870, "end_ms": 1109790, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是有一件事情你忘记了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 629, "start_ms": 1109790, "end_ms": 1111350, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "6月份的话是有618的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 630, "start_ms": 1111350, "end_ms": 1112470, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说你会发现", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 631, "start_ms": 1112470, "end_ms": 1114870, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "在这个里面有一个细节", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 632, "start_ms": 1114870, "end_ms": 1117150, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是比如说科选消费和避选消费这两者", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 633, "start_ms": 1117150, "end_ms": 1118430, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你稍微去看一看就知道了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 634, "start_ms": 1118430, "end_ms": 1119990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "科选消费付的12", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 635, "start_ms": 1120080, "end_ms": 1123320, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "狀態依舊有巨大的可提升空間", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 636, "start_ms": 1123320, "end_ms": 1125200, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後必須消費的話是6.5", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 637, "start_ms": 1125200, "end_ms": 1127000, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "為什麼這數字會這麼大呢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 638, "start_ms": 1127000, "end_ms": 1128280, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是原因非常的簡單", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 639, "start_ms": 1128280, "end_ms": 1129640, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "像2月份的時候是過年", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 640, "start_ms": 1129640, "end_ms": 1131480, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後這裡的話就是618", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 641, "start_ms": 1131480, "end_ms": 1133120, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這618過了以後你再過一個月", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 642, "start_ms": 1133120, "end_ms": 1135520, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "有可能你又看到這數據又不是很好了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 643, "start_ms": 1135520, "end_ms": 1137480, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這種可能性當然不是肯定的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 644, "start_ms": 1137480, "end_ms": 1140120, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但我相信之後的數據肯定會越來越好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 645, "start_ms": 1140120, "end_ms": 1142760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我們的經濟的未來肯定是越來越美好的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 646, "start_ms": 1142760, "end_ms": 1143920, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後再來看失業率", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 647, "start_ms": 1143920, "end_ms": 1145720, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "失業率的話基本上這數據就不用看", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 648, "start_ms": 1145720, "end_ms": 1148360, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我們這邊基本上沒有什麼太明顯的一個失業", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 649, "start_ms": 1148360, "end_ms": 1150040, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "都一直是在無左右", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 650, "start_ms": 1149890, "end_ms": 1151610, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后继续看整个经济指标", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 651, "start_ms": 1151610, "end_ms": 1153930, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是说今年其实对于整个GDP拉动最多的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 652, "start_ms": 1153930, "end_ms": 1154570, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "主要是出口", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 653, "start_ms": 1154570, "end_ms": 1156850, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "出口的表现其实是非常好的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 654, "start_ms": 1156850, "end_ms": 1158290, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其他的东西一般性", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 655, "start_ms": 1158290, "end_ms": 1159450, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是包括地产投资", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 656, "start_ms": 1159450, "end_ms": 1160290, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个都是复职", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 657, "start_ms": 1160290, "end_ms": 1162370, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "都在零位以下运行", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 658, "start_ms": 1162370, "end_ms": 1163610, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是我们通过这个东西", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 659, "start_ms": 1163610, "end_ms": 1165210, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "可以看到包括说设定消费", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 660, "start_ms": 1165210, "end_ms": 1167090, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "也基本上也在零位附近", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 661, "start_ms": 1167090, "end_ms": 1169890, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后制造业投资也不多或者什么", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 662, "start_ms": 1169890, "end_ms": 1172930, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那我们就基本可以看到整个经济的一个全贸", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 663, "start_ms": 1172930, "end_ms": 1175530, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大概的话就是出口生意非常好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 664, "start_ms": 1175530, "end_ms": 1177570, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "老外的话要货要的非常多", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 665, "start_ms": 1177570, "end_ms": 1178810, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说我们自己", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 666, "start_ms": 1178940, "end_ms": 1180340, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个上半年主要是在这里", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 667, "start_ms": 1180340, "end_ms": 1181180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后其他的话呢", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 668, "start_ms": 1181180, "end_ms": 1183540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们自己这边的口袋里还没两个钱", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 669, "start_ms": 1183540, "end_ms": 1184740, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大概是这样子", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 670, "start_ms": 1184740, "end_ms": 1186910, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其他一些数据就不跟大家解读了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 671, "start_ms": 1186910, "end_ms": 1190590, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是大家能够七七八八能够明白就可以", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 672, "start_ms": 1190590, "end_ms": 1194950, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后在今天的这个三点多钟的时候", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 673, "start_ms": 1194950, "end_ms": 1196710, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其实杨航说了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 674, "start_ms": 1196710, "end_ms": 1199510, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就当时这个收容数据也出来了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 675, "start_ms": 1199510, "end_ms": 1199830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "对吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 676, "start_ms": 1199830, "end_ms": 1201070, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "MEMR数据出来了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 677, "start_ms": 1201070, "end_ms": 1202710, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我们这个到之后再来跟大家解读", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 678, "start_ms": 1202710, "end_ms": 1203990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "今天时间不够了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 679, "start_ms": 1204720, "end_ms": 1208240, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "央行也說了要加大逆周期和跨周期的調節力度", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 680, "start_ms": 1208240, "end_ms": 1210960, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "鞏固拓展經濟穩中向好的勢頭", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 681, "start_ms": 1210960, "end_ms": 1215360, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "現在經濟穩中向好全部是經濟政策的一個關系", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 682, "start_ms": 1215360, "end_ms": 1218560, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是之前這個經濟都非常的好", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 683, "start_ms": 1218560, "end_ms": 1220160, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "現在還要再鞏固它", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 684, "start_ms": 1220160, "end_ms": 1221720, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "對不對 你們感受到了嗎", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 685, "start_ms": 1221720, "end_ms": 1225260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這種裡面說的一些東西", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 686, "start_ms": 1225260, "end_ms": 1226340, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我們就不跟大家講了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 687, "start_ms": 1226340, "end_ms": 1227820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "沒有什麼特殊的一些東西", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 688, "start_ms": 1227820, "end_ms": 1231260, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是說既然它要加大逆周期和跨周期的調節力度", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 689, "start_ms": 1231260, "end_ms": 1232900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "對市場來說都是好事", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 690, "start_ms": 1232980, "end_ms": 1234820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后再来看一下业绩大铺位的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 691, "start_ms": 1234820, "end_ms": 1236660, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "QR经理润环璧增长是翻倍", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 692, "start_ms": 1236660, "end_ms": 1240100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是要注意这种东西当时出来的时候", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 693, "start_ms": 1240100, "end_ms": 1242060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "有的时候我们打辛苦的时候", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 694, "start_ms": 1242060, "end_ms": 1243180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大家经常可以看到", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 695, "start_ms": 1243180, "end_ms": 1244780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是说我会给大家写一下", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 696, "start_ms": 1244780, "end_ms": 1246980, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大致的一个开盘的一个价格", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 697, "start_ms": 1246980, "end_ms": 1249580, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "或者大概大致的一个获利的一个情况", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 698, "start_ms": 1249580, "end_ms": 1250620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个都会跟大家写", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 699, "start_ms": 1250620, "end_ms": 1251900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "现在你去看", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 700, "start_ms": 1251900, "end_ms": 1254060, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "当时写的时候大铺位在这个点上", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 701, "start_ms": 1254060, "end_ms": 1255900, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其实就已经不算太便宜了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 702, "start_ms": 1255900, "end_ms": 1258420, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是现在跑到这里去", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 703, "start_ms": 1258420, "end_ms": 1259980, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你就知道这炒作", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 704, "start_ms": 1259980, "end_ms": 1261860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它其实有的时候大票", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 705, "start_ms": 1261870, "end_ms": 1265030, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "也會有今年的特徵就是大票也會炒作", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 706, "start_ms": 1265030, "end_ms": 1266670, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大票一樣炒到天上去", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 707, "start_ms": 1266670, "end_ms": 1267950, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後再一滴寂寞", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 708, "start_ms": 1267950, "end_ms": 1270030, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "結果和這個其實炒零碗票", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 709, "start_ms": 1270030, "end_ms": 1271510, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實沒有什麼太大差別", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 710, "start_ms": 1271510, "end_ms": 1272750, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這都也都很貴了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 711, "start_ms": 1272750, "end_ms": 1276070, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它就算說是這個利潤增長百分之百", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 712, "start_ms": 1276070, "end_ms": 1277590, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "也就是大概", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 713, "start_ms": 1277590, "end_ms": 1279750, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這麼上半年半年度嘛", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 714, "start_ms": 1279750, "end_ms": 1280790, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "也就是來個億嘛", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 715, "start_ms": 1280790, "end_ms": 1282190, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你到一年的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 716, "start_ms": 1282190, "end_ms": 1284110, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "能夠有個30個億不得了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 717, "start_ms": 1284110, "end_ms": 1286190, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那你看看你自己有多少的這個市值", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 718, "start_ms": 1286190, "end_ms": 1287470, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "嚇死個人對吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 719, "start_ms": 1287470, "end_ms": 1290300, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "出來的話至少有八九十倍的脾氣吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 720, "start_ms": 1291580, "end_ms": 1294540, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "不跌吗 肯定要跌 这无非就涨得多了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 721, "start_ms": 1294540, "end_ms": 1297700, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后像百位城储上半年是3000多", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 722, "start_ms": 1297700, "end_ms": 1299100, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是这里有个问题", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 723, "start_ms": 1299100, "end_ms": 1300940, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个二阶岛开始下来了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 724, "start_ms": 1300940, "end_ms": 1303020, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你这里的话增速是往上走的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 725, "start_ms": 1303020, "end_ms": 1305740, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这里增速慢慢的趋滑了 趋滑很正常", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 726, "start_ms": 1305740, "end_ms": 1309180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "以后你可以看到三季度基本上就是它的最高值", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 727, "start_ms": 1309180, "end_ms": 1311620, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "甚至三季度都不一定能维持到最高值", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 728, "start_ms": 1311620, "end_ms": 1312860, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "四季度它就要回落了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 729, "start_ms": 1312860, "end_ms": 1315180, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因为它的便宜库层基本上消耗光了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 730, "start_ms": 1315180, "end_ms": 1317740, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以现在这个东西 你就看到的其实就是个顶", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 731, "start_ms": 1317740, "end_ms": 1323840, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是你现在看到的其实就是个顶", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 732, "start_ms": 1323870, "end_ms": 1326070, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他的這個峰值其實已經出來了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 733, "start_ms": 1326070, "end_ms": 1327470, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "後面就算後面兩個基督說", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 734, "start_ms": 1327470, "end_ms": 1329110, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "業績好了他怎麼跌", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 735, "start_ms": 1329110, "end_ms": 1331350, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你看這個市場不會價值投資", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 736, "start_ms": 1331350, "end_ms": 1332990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "PE不是只有12倍嗎", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 737, "start_ms": 1332990, "end_ms": 1334590, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "弄台P12倍他怎麼跌", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 738, "start_ms": 1334590, "end_ms": 1336190, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "對 你已經看到他的頂了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 739, "start_ms": 1336190, "end_ms": 1337910, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個景氣投資就是這麼回事", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 740, "start_ms": 1337910, "end_ms": 1338950, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一旦景氣反轉", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 741, "start_ms": 1338950, "end_ms": 1340950, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一旦景氣他的二階島回來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 742, "start_ms": 1340950, "end_ms": 1342550, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "掉下來 那你就別想了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 743, "start_ms": 1342550, "end_ms": 1343910, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那後面肯定是跌的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 744, "start_ms": 1343910, "end_ms": 1345070, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個要去注意", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 745, "start_ms": 1345070, "end_ms": 1345790, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就這裡你說", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 746, "start_ms": 1345790, "end_ms": 1347430, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他馬上在反彈上去不會的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 747, "start_ms": 1347430, "end_ms": 1349150, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他這裡就會震盪", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 748, "start_ms": 1349150, "end_ms": 1350230, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "正常這裡就是震盪", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 749, "start_ms": 1350230, "end_ms": 1352030, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "震盪以後弄弄他又掉下去了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 750, "start_ms": 1352030, "end_ms": 1353670, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說這種", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 751, "start_ms": 1353630, "end_ms": 1355310, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "平時就不要再去看了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 752, "start_ms": 1355310, "end_ms": 1358630, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然後再去看看比如說這個是這個旅", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 753, "start_ms": 1358630, "end_ms": 1362710, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "因為現在的天氣是比較熱了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 754, "start_ms": 1362710, "end_ms": 1364310, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以說我們可以去看一下", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 755, "start_ms": 1364310, "end_ms": 1364830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "像這個旅", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 756, "start_ms": 1364830, "end_ms": 1369760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個當然旅業", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 757, "start_ms": 1369760, "end_ms": 1370600, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "明太旅業", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 758, "start_ms": 1370600, "end_ms": 1372520, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "現在的狀況是這樣子", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 759, "start_ms": 1372520, "end_ms": 1373680, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它比較好的是", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 760, "start_ms": 1373680, "end_ms": 1375400, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "第一個中暴業績就比較不錯", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 761, "start_ms": 1375400, "end_ms": 1377200, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "當中暴已經預告過了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 762, "start_ms": 1377200, "end_ms": 1378400, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "業績是大幅度上升的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 763, "start_ms": 1378400, "end_ms": 1380120, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "而且這裡居然還沒怎麼漲", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 764, "start_ms": 1380110, "end_ms": 1381030, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那有点意思", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 765, "start_ms": 1381030, "end_ms": 1383470, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后对于说这种周期股的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 766, "start_ms": 1383470, "end_ms": 1385270, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "一般来说我们去看PB会多一点", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 767, "start_ms": 1385270, "end_ms": 1387070, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "PB的话1.02还是不错的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 768, "start_ms": 1387070, "end_ms": 1388950, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个说估值也不是很高", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 769, "start_ms": 1388950, "end_ms": 1390350, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它说整体的在手订单", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 770, "start_ms": 1390350, "end_ms": 1391550, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "大概是1.5个月以上", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 771, "start_ms": 1391550, "end_ms": 1395550, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "按照说这个就是行业内的一个状况的话", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 772, "start_ms": 1395550, "end_ms": 1397550, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它部分产品的排场下三个月以上", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 773, "start_ms": 1397550, "end_ms": 1401870, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以说以现在的这个行业内一般来说", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 774, "start_ms": 1401870, "end_ms": 1403750, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是如果说有1.5个月的一个整体", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 775, "start_ms": 1403750, "end_ms": 1406670, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "和三个月的一个这个部分的一些", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 776, "start_ms": 1406670, "end_ms": 1408710, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "可能是一些高端产品或者怎么样子的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 777, "start_ms": 1409020, "end_ms": 1412820, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这种拍摄器的话其实生意还算是不错的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 778, "start_ms": 1412820, "end_ms": 1414340, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "生意是相当相当不错的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 779, "start_ms": 1414430, "end_ms": 1417990, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以這個時候你可以看到履駕對它的一個下跌的一個影響", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 780, "start_ms": 1417990, "end_ms": 1419110, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實是非常有限的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 781, "start_ms": 1419110, "end_ms": 1420950, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個公司倒是也可以看兩眼的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 782, "start_ms": 1420950, "end_ms": 1422670, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "當然這個公司絕對不是推薦", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 783, "start_ms": 1422670, "end_ms": 1423830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你可以稍微去看看的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 784, "start_ms": 1423830, "end_ms": 1426390, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "它既然明確說我後面有這麼多的訂單", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 785, "start_ms": 1426390, "end_ms": 1427230, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "單子都在", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 786, "start_ms": 1427230, "end_ms": 1428510, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "所以這個還是可以的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 787, "start_ms": 1428510, "end_ms": 1430470, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "走勢各方面都還是不錯的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 788, "start_ms": 1430470, "end_ms": 1431830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "技術面上也很不錯", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 789, "start_ms": 1431830, "end_ms": 1434830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個有一種小青龍的味道在這裡面", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 790, "start_ms": 1434830, "end_ms": 1436870, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "後面不知道這裡會不會走到這裡", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 791, "start_ms": 1436870, "end_ms": 1438470, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "會不會有這個方量", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 792, "start_ms": 1438470, "end_ms": 1439830, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這裡會不會有方量的一個動作", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 793, "start_ms": 1439830, "end_ms": 1441950, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "方量就起來會主聲一小波", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 794, "start_ms": 1441950, "end_ms": 1442870, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "最後結束掉", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 795, "start_ms": 1442910, "end_ms": 1445550, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这种周期股也就只能拉一波就走", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 796, "start_ms": 1445550, "end_ms": 1446750, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你也不能去拿很久", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 797, "start_ms": 1447970, "end_ms": 1450490, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "好 其他的受容我们等等再说吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 798, "start_ms": 1450490, "end_ms": 1452850, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "这个东西我正在去", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 799, "start_ms": 1452850, "end_ms": 1455250, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我要去挖掘其中的一些亮点", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 800, "start_ms": 1455250, "end_ms": 1456370, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "然后来跟大家讲", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 801, "start_ms": 1456370, "end_ms": 1458690, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我目前我这还没有仔细去看", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 802, "start_ms": 1459450, "end_ms": 1461570, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "等到之后再跟大家去讲吧", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 803, "start_ms": 1462980, "end_ms": 1465740, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "好 其他的就不多说了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 804, "start_ms": 1466020, "end_ms": 1468140, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "明天的话应该是明天16号", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 805, "start_ms": 1468140, "end_ms": 1469940, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "明天打星谷一定要打", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 806, "start_ms": 1469940, "end_ms": 1471940, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "具体的整个打星的一个攻略", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 807, "start_ms": 1471940, "end_ms": 1472780, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "我还是一样的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 808, "start_ms": 1473490, "end_ms": 1475210, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "在這個盤中會寫給大家", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 809, "start_ms": 1475210, "end_ms": 1476890, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "到那個時候大家來看一下就行了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 810, "start_ms": 1477530, "end_ms": 1478930, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其他的就不多說了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 811, "start_ms": 1478930, "end_ms": 1480010, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "就是我們現在的話", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 812, "start_ms": 1480010, "end_ms": 1481650, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "反正你不去追高", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 813, "start_ms": 1481650, "end_ms": 1484210, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "不去那些特別擁擠的一個方向", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 814, "start_ms": 1484210, "end_ms": 1485570, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "那他現在的出清", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 815, "start_ms": 1485570, "end_ms": 1487250, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你等到出清結束以後", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 816, "start_ms": 1487250, "end_ms": 1490250, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個市場才能夠說整個見底", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 817, "start_ms": 1490250, "end_ms": 1491570, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "等到他們沒有出清結束", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 818, "start_ms": 1491570, "end_ms": 1494330, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個市場是很難徹底去見底的", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 819, "start_ms": 1494330, "end_ms": 1496730, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "但是有一些低位的老燈的方向", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 820, "start_ms": 1496730, "end_ms": 1498210, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "還有一些低估的方向", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 821, "start_ms": 1498210, "end_ms": 1499890, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "其實已經非常值得一看", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 822, "start_ms": 1500000, "end_ms": 1502240, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "當然了 這裡注意 他們前面跌的多了", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 823, "start_ms": 1502240, "end_ms": 1503880, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這裡你看 起來了之後", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 824, "start_ms": 1503880, "end_ms": 1506760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "等到市場跌的多了 他們也會有回彩", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 825, "start_ms": 1506760, "end_ms": 1507840, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個回彩也是一個", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 826, "start_ms": 1507840, "end_ms": 1510600, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "你說這裡沒趕上 沒關係 後面還會有機會", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 827, "start_ms": 1510600, "end_ms": 1511760, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "他們還會再上來", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 828, "start_ms": 1511760, "end_ms": 1515080, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "這個下半年的市場是一個再平衡的一個過程", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 829, "start_ms": 1515080, "end_ms": 1517920, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "好吧 好了 那今天的節目也就到這邊", "confidence_score": null}, {"segment_index": 830, "start_ms": 1517920, "end_ms": 1519520, "speaker_label": "speaker_0", "text": "祝大家投資愉快 拜拜", "confidence_score": null}], "chunks": [{"id": 69, "chunk_index": 0, "start_ms": 370, "end_ms": 89180, "topic": "880823", "transcript_text": "大家晚上好 歡迎收看鷹眼看盤看開始本次節目之前 首先要提示大家股市有風險 入序需謹慎 節目中期到的案例和標的 均勢歷史回顧 不構成投資建議 好 我們今天視頻可能會稍微短一點 首先來看一下今天的盤面 盤面當中我們看到今天整個分值是比較低的 這個是今天看起來整個市場比較差的一面 但好的一面今天漲的個戶還是比較多 3351個在漲 2098個在低 那這到底是怎麼回事呢 我們可以看到 各個各大寬機 其實表現其實都是比較弱的 像中正1000 國正2000 然後包括中正500 其實基本上都跌了一點幾左右 但反過來說 微盤股是漲的 全中位數是漲的 微盤股的話 其實很久之前就提醒大家了 就是說你會發現 當說整個市場的槓桿率 最高的一個地方 比如說像半導體 雲期間 或者同性设备 他们是杠杆最高的一个地方 出现这种类似 因为今天又崩溃了对吧 又出现了这种崩溃的这个状况的时候 一部分的这个量化资金 它就会回到微盘里面去 为什么 因为微盘里面它没有杠杆 微盘 而且是拥挤度 在今年的话 算是拥挤度最低的一个方向之一了 所以说在这里面 它没有杂盘力量 因为跌过一大波了 所以说它没有什么杂判令 但是你在其他的这些东西里面 就有可能是为什么呢 有可能会被 比如说去钢杆的一部分的资金被砸 哪里在去钢杆呢 大家也可以看一下 像融资融券我们点两融前景 我们可以特别明显的看得到", "ocr_text": "系统 功能 深度 报价 分析扩展市场行情 特灵交易 资讯工具 帮助 交易策略 发现 市场 问小达 TQ策略已开启 微盘股 交易信息 18:59:03周三 行情 资讯 交易 服务\n分时1分钟5分钟15分钟30分钟60分钟 日线周线月线10分钟45日线季线年线5秒15秒多周期更多 复权复盘 回溯 统计 画线 F10 标记-自选 返回 880823微盘股\n微盘股（日线前复权）MA5:6071.69MA10:6136.66MA20:6196.88MA60:6870.85MA200:6821.92MA888 7824.64 A股成交 25868.31亿\n股成交 2.23亿\n7500 国债成交 26472.73亿\n基金成交 5392.79亿\n7250 最新指数 6165.16\n7000 今日开盘 6078.38\n昨日收盘 6085.82\n6750 指数涨跌 79.34\n指数涨幅 1.30%\n6500 平均涨幅 1.27%\n6250 指数换手 2.60%\n指数振幅 167.71/2.76%\n6000 总成交额 174.18亿\n总成交量 2268.6万\n5719.15 5750 最高指数 6226.08\n5500 最低指数 6058.37\n指数量比 0.97\n5250 涨停轨迹目 风格加权成份股围\n5000 涨家.涨停 337/3跌家.跌停 57/0\n主力净额目 -6997万 -0%\n4750 10日主力净额 3.64亿 0%\n4500 14:55 6159.62 557.0万\n14:55 6160.10 454.0万\n14:55 6160.34 479.0万\nAMO-TDX(5.10）AM0W:1741828.50MA5:1787500.25MA10:1856558.25 14:55 6159.70 544.0万\n45000 14:55 6159.61 465.0万\n14:56 6159.39 645.0万\n30000 14:56 6158.81 766.0万\n15000 14:56 6158.66 728.0万\nX100 14:56 6158